abstract: Wisconsin-Stevens Point beats State University of New York at Geneseo, 5-1, in NCAA Division III hockey tournament semifinals; other college hockey news noted.

headline.main: Geneseo Falls to Wisconsin-Stevens Point in Semifinals

keywords.value: State University of New York at Geneseo
keywords.name: organizations

snippet: The State University of New York at Geneseo’s pursuit of its first N.C.A.A. Division III title came to a halt with a 5-1 drubbing by Wisconsin-Stevens Point in the semifinals in Lake Placid, N.Y.
lead_paragraph: The State University of New York at Geneseo’s pursuit of its first N.C.A.A. Division III title came to a halt with a 5-1 drubbing by Wisconsin-Stevens Point in the semifinals in Lake Placid, N.Y.
